entries.s_f49a789f: I'm here to wax the matter inducer.
entries.s_cbb1bec7: Clean the antimatter condenser? Well...yeah I suppose it's probably getting a little jammed with all of the work we've been putting it through. You can find the Snaff Grease in the back. Hurry up though, there's probably a bunch of ships waiting to be fueled up.
